{
  "title": "Mildly Sour Uruguayan Tobiko Ceviche",
  "description": "A refreshing and healthy Uruguayan dish featuring tobiko, perfect for a post-workout snack, with a mildly sour taste and a shattering texture, served in an agave leaf vessel.",
  "cuisine": "Uruguayan",
  "diet": [
